| Category                          | AWS service                        | GCP service                                              | Notes                                                                                                                              |
| --------------------------------- | ---------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Serverless containers / HTTP apps | AWS App Runner / ECS Fargate       | Cloud Run                                                | All run containers with autoscaling; Cloud Run and App Runner are closest in “fully managed HTTP service” behavior.                |
| Serverless functions              | AWS Lambda                         | Cloud Functions                                          | Event-driven functions; Lambda has deep AWS integration, Cloud Functions integrates tightly with GCP and Firebase.                 |
| General compute (VMs)             | EC2                                | Compute Engine                                           | Both provide VMs of various sizes and families.                                                                                    |
| Managed Kubernetes                | EKS                                | GKE                                                      | Both manage control plane and integrate with their respective ecosystems; GKE is often seen as slightly more “batteries included”. |
| HTTP/API gateway                  | Amazon API Gateway / ALB (HTTP)    | API Gateway / Cloud Endpoints                            | Front door for REST/HTTP APIs and LLM backends.                                                                                    |
| Object storage                    | S3                                 | Cloud Storage                                            | Durable, scalable object stores with lifecycle, versioning, and encryption.                                                        |
| Relational database               | RDS (Aurora, etc.)                 | Cloud SQL / AlloyDB                                      | Managed relational DB engines.                                                                                                     |
| NoSQL / document                  | DynamoDB                           | Firestore / Cloud Bigtable                               | Low‑latency, scalable NoSQL; DynamoDB vs Firestore is the most common pairing.                                                     |
| LLM / GenAI platform              | Amazon Bedrock / SageMaker         | Vertex AI (incl. Gemini)                                 | Managed GenAI/LLM endpoints, safety tools, and orchestration.                                                                      |
| Identity & access                 | IAM, AWS Organizations             | IAM, Cloud Identity, Resource Manager                    | Both provide fine‑grained IAM, org hierarchy, and policies.                                                                        |
| Key management                    | KMS                                | Cloud KMS                                                | Centralized key management and encryption integration.                                                                             |
| Network isolation                 | VPC, Security Groups, NACLs        | VPC, Firewall Rules                                      | Private networks, subnets, routing, and firewalling.                                                                               |
| WAF & edge security               | AWS WAF, AWS Shield, CloudFront    | Cloud Armor, Cloud CDN                                   | L7 protections and edge distributions.                                                                                             |
| Logging & monitoring              | CloudWatch, CloudTrail             | Cloud Logging, Cloud Monitoring, Cloud Audit Logs        | Metrics, logs, traces, and API audit trails.                                                                                       |
| Security posture / findings       | Security Hub, GuardDuty, Inspector | Security Command Center, Cloud DLP, Web Security Scanner | Centralized security and vulnerability insights.                                                                                   |
